      "transcript": "I'm sorry you're stuck. Let's get you set up. What device are you using, iPhone, Android, or computer? And are you seeing an error message or just not finding the 2FA option? Absolutely, I can walk you through it. Are you doing this on iPhone, Android, or a computer? And are you trying to enable 2FA in the app or on our website?"
